"     see \"Ethinyl estradiol and desogestrel: Drug information\"",
"    </a>",
"    )",
"   </p>",
"   <div class=\"list ubnlist drugH1Div drugBrandNames\" id=\"F168201\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
